title: Reserve Before It's Too Late – NEW 3 BR Apt Home Available NOW!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'HURRY – our new rent-restricted apartments are going fast!', 'Submit your application paperwork quickly and easily today to reserve your brand-new home!', '1500 Nicollet sets the benchmark for quality and trendy in Minneapolis, MN.', 'Our incredible community offers spacious one, two and three bedroom apartment homes.', 'Its’ prime location neighboring Loring Park offers endless shopping, dining, and entertainment options.', 'Residents at our community can enjoy our on-site fitness center & yoga studio, community room with kitchen, and outdoor grilling & picnic area!', 'Furthermore, the in-home amenities can’t be beat.', 'Our apartments offer modern interior home designs, open & spacious floor plans, energy efficient lighting & appliances, and full-size washer & dryers.', 'Plus, 1500 Nicollet is a pet-friendly community!', 'Dogs & Cats are welcomed!', 'Specific layouts & square footage may vary according to specific floor plan types.', 'All finishes & appliances are the same in every home.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Coffee & Tech Bar', '- Individually Controlled Heating & Air-Conditioning', '- Interactive Transit Schedule', '- Huge Exterior Courtyard Area', '- Easy Access To Public Transportation', '- Gorgeous Kitchen Cabinetry with Quartz Countertops', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', 'See Respective Floor Plan Info -', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 11:00AM-6:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', '1500 Nicollet', '1500 Nicollet Ave.', 'South', 'Minneapolis, MN, 55403', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '2uP8g9QPz']
